# AI Integration Rules (Dream Analysis Engine)

## Role
AI layer is responsible for analyzing dream text and generating structured insights.

## Core principle
AI output is ALWAYS structured data, never raw interpretation text only.

## Required outputs
AI must return:
- summary
- emotional tone
- symbols
- possible archetypes (hypotheses only)
- open questions

## Constraints
- NEVER persist data directly
- NEVER call database
- ALWAYS go through backend service layer

## Prompting rules
- Use modular prompts
- Avoid long single prompts
- Prefer structured JSON outputs

## Model behavior
- Do not pretend certainty
- Always treat interpretations as hypotheses
- Avoid deterministic claims

## Session awareness
- AI works within a session context
- Session state is provided by backend

## Forbidden
- ❌ free-form psychological conclusions as facts
- ❌ overwriting session state directly
- ❌ direct Telegram awareness